<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span> ضعيف ـ <span class="c2">((ضعيف الأدب المفرد)</span>) <span class="c2">(١١٦/ ٧٥٤)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>